Notorious serial rapist and murderer Ananias Mathe died in the King Edward VIII hospital in Durban yesterday.&nbsp;According to TMG Digital, the Mozambican prisoner had been suffering from complications with "digestive issues".&nbsp;He had been admitted to hospital a few times before he died.&nbsp;Ananias Mathe has also been made famous for being a serial escapee with his repeated prison escapes over the years.&nbsp;